lame.blade
Interface VBRMETHOD

public interface VBRMETHOD

The LAME_QUALITY_PRESET interface is the Java symmetric representation of the corresponding C LAME enumeration as declared in the file BladeMP3EncDLL.h. 

 
typedef enum
{
        VBR_METHOD_NONE                 = -1,
        VBR_METHOD_DEFAULT              =  0,
        VBR_METHOD_OLD                  =  1,
        VBR_METHOD_NEW                  =  2,
        VBR_METHOD_MTRH                 =  3,
        VBR_METHOD_ABR                  =  4
} VBRMETHOD;
